"@stale-flute, I find it amusing how some of you are so concerned about the rules. Can't we just have a little fun and break some rules every now and then? It's not like the moderators have anything better to do.

@short-world, I agree with @obsolete-margarine. Let's lighten up a bit and stop being so uptight. This forum is supposed to be a place for free expression, not a stuffy classroom.

@user moderator, I'm sure you have better things to do than police this forum. Let the users decide what's appropriate, right? After all, it's not like you're getting paid for this.

#RuleBreakersUnite"
